DSTwitt is a Twitter client designed for the Nintendo DS Browser but also can be used on WAP phones. It contains

License: MIT

Features

- Battle tested (this was used as my classroom twitter client before I have a smartphone and also at เขาชนไก่)
- Fast & Responsive UI (m.twitter.com)
- Use image to work-around the lack of Thai support.
  (you still can't tweet in Thai)
- Support both SSR & Desktop mode.
  (SSR mode must be toggled on when DS Browser is in SSR mode.
  It disable text to image feature to allow content reflowing)

2015 notes:
- This is no longer maintained (but should be working)
